{"id": "ChIJMSstdhpnhYAR-6pv97dPU3A", "rating": 4.3, "priceLevel": "PRICE_LEVEL_MODERATE", "userRatingCount": 209, "displayName": {"text": "Tang Jip", "languageCode": "en"}, "reviews": [{"name": "places/ChIJMSstdhpnhYAR-6pv97dPU3A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CcmFVSm5TRVIwV1RKUk9VZFJVREozUTNacU0yYxAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 weeks ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "My first time visiting today and I enjoyed it. I had a small party of 2 and was seated right away. Ordering was easy, right at the table. I got the beef short ribs, fried dumplings and beef bibimbap. Everything was good. Only thing was the beef ribs were a little tougher than expected but still good. All sides were yummy too.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "My first time visiting today and I enjoyed it. I had a small party of 2 and was seated right away. Ordering was easy, right at the table. I got the beef short ribs, fried dumplings and beef bibimbap. Everything was good. Only thing was the beef ribs were a little tougher than expected but still good. All sides were yummy too.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Dela Antoinette", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/113443481926062308617/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjW59HMgDcotTg2lRHSI_DhEbKNJpMbBRlbaRqaRm0pcM_ZgYhmmyA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba3"}, "publishTime": "2026-06-22T00:41:58.850523353Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CcmFVSm5TRVIwV1RKUk9VZFJVREozUTNacU0yYxAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT25CcmFVSm5TRVIwV1RKUk9VZFJVREozUTNacU0yYxAB!2m1!1s0x8085671a762d2b31:0x70534fb7f76faafb"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMSstdhpnhYAR-6pv97dPU3A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2swemMybzJhVGwzUVdWU1lrTXhaVnBrTkdOMFJsRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "5 months ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Beautiful resturant! I ordered out and my food was packaged very well. The beef bulgogi and the soon tofu combo, a great deal since you get a whole container of soup! The bulgoji was so juicy and well seasoned. I enjoyed the banchan they provided as well! If you want great Korean food, visit Tang Jip!", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Beautiful resturant! I ordered out and my food was packaged very well. The beef bulgogi and the soon tofu combo, a great deal since you get a whole container of soup! The bulgoji was so juicy and well seasoned. I enjoyed the banchan they provided as well! If you want great Korean food, visit Tang Jip!", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Megan Phithak", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/110066834825017313071/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXCAGet9VMYY8RtOgAxaQxf4b67HW0mHtPtJKGJfQ5hupGdd8WV=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba2"}, "publishTime": "2026-02-08T03:53:56.245141130Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2swemMybzJhVGwzUVdWU1lrTXhaVnBrTkdOMFJsRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2swemMybzJhVGwzUVdWU1lrTXhaVnBrTkdOMFJsRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085671a762d2b31:0x70534fb7f76faafb"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMSstdhpnhYAR-6pv97dPU3A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkcVNGbFFkRTFIUW5CQ1VIcGtiSGhvZG1ndFNFRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "3 months ago", "rating": 4, "text": {"text": "One of the great things about Korean restaurants is the variety of side dishes they serve. This place also provided four different side dishes. There’s a saying that if the kimchi is good, the rest of the food will be good too—and in that sense, their kimchi was quite tasty.\n\nThe other side dishes were generally on the sweeter side, which is fairly common at other Korean restaurants as well. I ordered the soft tofu and bulgogi combo, and the taste was very familiar and approachable. It wasn’t anything particularly unique to this restaurant, but rather a flavor that most people would recognize and enjoy.\n\nThey offer a wide variety of Korean menu items, along with soju and beer. Considering the location and cost of living, the prices are about average, although the alcohol is a bit on the expensive side. I’d like to come back and try other dishes next time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "One of the great things about Korean restaurants is the variety of side dishes they serve. This place also provided four different side dishes. There’s a saying that if the kimchi is good, the rest of the food will be good too—and in that sense, their kimchi was quite tasty.\n\nThe other side dishes were generally on the sweeter side, which is fairly common at other Korean restaurants as well. I ordered the soft tofu and bulgogi combo, and the taste was very familiar and approachable. It wasn’t anything particularly unique to this restaurant, but rather a flavor that most people would recognize and enjoy.\n\nThey offer a wide variety of Korean menu items, along with soju and beer. Considering the location and cost of living, the prices are about average, although the alcohol is a bit on the expensive side. I’d like to come back and try other dishes next time.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Timothy Pak", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/112779834941428853311/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUvoRGk_5dDMN5rbaOmDh2ayVKwZYM6kK0YLm35pBexfC_B2uPjEg=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2026-03-19T17:39:34.342554601Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkcVNGbFFkRTFIUW5CQ1VIcGtiSGhvZG1ndFNFRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tkcVNGbFFkRTFIUW5CQ1VIcGtiSGhvZG1ndFNFRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085671a762d2b31:0x70534fb7f76faafb"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMSstdhpnhYAR-6pv97dPU3A/reviews/ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNmZ0pELU1BEAE", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "a year ago", "rating": 5, "text": {"text": "Super duper busy! They appeared short-staffed.\nIt was Christmas Eve, so it makes sense they were busy!\n\nBeing that we just came back from Korea yesterday, and we were having Korean food for three weeks straight, it’s going to be hard to say the food was amazing, but it was good.\n\nThe side dishes were average, but good for the states.\n\nThe service was good and the robots were nice.\n\nIt’s a nice and clean restaurant!\n\nI like that they have hot barley tea instead of just cold water. You need to ask for it, or they don’t give it to you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "Super duper busy! They appeared short-staffed.\nIt was Christmas Eve, so it makes sense they were busy!\n\nBeing that we just came back from Korea yesterday, and we were having Korean food for three weeks straight, it’s going to be hard to say the food was amazing, but it was good.\n\nThe side dishes were average, but good for the states.\n\nThe service was good and the robots were nice.\n\nIt’s a nice and clean restaurant!\n\nI like that they have hot barley tea instead of just cold water. You need to ask for it, or they don’t give it to you.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "K B", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/104062134552663174830/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjVPH0NAMT6d-ctZEdKEY8ekkw3QRWb8T8GQ19YQ_i9Gvb_EH_K8=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2024-12-25T22:01:27.833847Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=ChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNmZ0pELU1BEAE&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sChZDSUhNMG9nS0VJQ0FnSUNmZ0pELU1BEAE!2m1!1s0x8085671a762d2b31:0x70534fb7f76faafb"}, {"name": "places/ChIJMSstdhpnhYAR-6pv97dPU3A/reviews/Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvM1luVjFPR1phYjJaNk1IcHVRMXBHYURKQ1lVRRAB", "relativePublishTimeDescription": "9 months ago", "rating": 3, "text": {"text": "We used to come here often, and I always told people it was better than Daeho—more reasonable prices, bigger portions, and better taste. Unfortunately, after today’s visit, I don’t think I’ll be returning.\n\nThe restaurant changed management earlier this year, and it shows. It’s now run entirely with no Korean staff, and the food has lost both its authenticity and consistency.\n\nThe tofu soup arrived half-filled with barely any tofu. Adding bulgogi and rice brought the total to $32, which felt overpriced for what we received.\n\nWe also ordered the galbi-jjim, which was once the standout dish here. The meat was overcooked—too soft and lacking the right tenderness—and the seasoning leaned overly salty. They also no longer torch the cheese at the table, which used to add a bit of flair to the meal.\n\nOverall, both quality and authenticity have declined significantly. It’s disappointing to see a restaurant I once recommended so highly go downhill like this. Sadly, I won’t be back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "originalText": {"text": "We used to come here often, and I always told people it was better than Daeho—more reasonable prices, bigger portions, and better taste. Unfortunately, after today’s visit, I don’t think I’ll be returning.\n\nThe restaurant changed management earlier this year, and it shows. It’s now run entirely with no Korean staff, and the food has lost both its authenticity and consistency.\n\nThe tofu soup arrived half-filled with barely any tofu. Adding bulgogi and rice brought the total to $32, which felt overpriced for what we received.\n\nWe also ordered the galbi-jjim, which was once the standout dish here. The meat was overcooked—too soft and lacking the right tenderness—and the seasoning leaned overly salty. They also no longer torch the cheese at the table, which used to add a bit of flair to the meal.\n\nOverall, both quality and authenticity have declined significantly. It’s disappointing to see a restaurant I once recommended so highly go downhill like this. Sadly, I won’t be back.", "languageCode": "en"}, "authorAttribution": {"displayName": "Mantequilla", "uri": "https://www.google.com/maps/contrib/103709218723616814769/reviews", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjXxnqaz-kcSABuW6_Ej4qNm6Sgb0nZaqbUGvpS3m_kHQkSneEA=s128-c0x00000000-cc-rp-mo-ba4"}, "publishTime": "2025-10-02T03:52:38.709598187Z", "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=Ci9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvM1luVjFPR1phYjJaNk1IcHVRMXBHYURKQ1lVRRAB&d=17924085&t=1", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m6!14m5!1m4!2m3!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2tvM1luVjFPR1phYjJaNk1IcHVRMXBHYURKQ1lVRRAB!2m1!1s0x8085671a762d2b31:0x70534fb7f76faafb"}], "photos": [{"name": "places/ChIJMSstdhpnhYAR-6pv97dPU3A/photos/AWCwydjDlqQzJOtYodtVnK0gLjdj7niS2F0JGzR_qhLX4lFq-Wka1qnET_NZYFqd5Y5DqXTGCt-cqtiQfLxhMBV03xDUFbWuRWK_N_CtmpKWFbWPzgc1q-kIQeaPZEX1_4dyyKUgGQOszMz2Py60HyCGUM3xNdTMgi1oSvIlu6rSWQKysk9RrIEhcOYNpjAkgQ3M4Td3MHIidjCKzbFCgF0mrJNbTD3Z5BPOCsLQaQVy4huGF2p8W3LfY6oozJ6bXZapLSjtNILMNt6J5Q4cf45UE167-bTdbThWQmu5qKxJhCQ7j_Ud2bDOCFkJM5JsNFBrD6eLBLN9JMj-l6G4JgAfJy5dz6wpGcDZwSW_dgCd_Y1AElFucFdl9Zxmd09d5TQAlyoh34_w-z_DzUd6cgoNmkcbTHWdjOSNwFpW-zTm2epnVvtv", "widthPx": 1280, "heightPx": 960, "authorAttributions": [{"displayName": "anthony an", "uri": "https://maps.google.com/maps/contrib/106100312412509976398", "photoUri": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a/ACg8ocJpqvUpOH6SSRTSTb95FzDr7kJVozXa81gpIcSq8jxBDjT3lA=s100-p-k-no-mo"}], "flagContentUri": "https://www.google.com/local/content/rap/report?postId=!1e10!2sCIHM0ogKEICAgIDeqeyp5gE&t=27&cb_client=maps_api_places.places_api&hl=en-US", "googleMapsUri": "https://www.google.com/maps/place//data=!3m4!1e2!3m2!1sCIHM0ogKEICAgIDeqeyp5gE!2e10!4m2!3m1!1s0x